result.name: Genki Sushi

reviews.text:
Good sushi and good variety. Same to every other Genki sushi store in terms of sushi. 

Nice staff, very responsive and good service. They sometimes seem to be short staffed yet does not always get crowded except during exhibition days. 

Good vibe and atmosphere. Good the location too.
Place is good not too long to wait. Food is fresh. Size ok

Nice place to visit except lunch as too many people waiting. The sears are comfortable. Service is great in other time sessions. Can walk to the ferry pier and appreciate the Victoria harbour site seeing.

I was excited to have sushi in Hong Kong. My coworker and I decided to try this place. We got in and saw that it was a conveyor belt sushi however there was not much coming around. They did allow is to order what we wanted, but it ended up being mediocre at best. We were there around 4 pm so maybe it was because we early or before the dinner rush. I doubt that I would go back the next time I am in HK.
Fun place for lunch or dinner.   We are visiting from USA and stopped here for lunch.  Very busy at lunch but staff was very welcoming.  And who doesn't like convayor belt sishi!
